snippet.title: Sega CD - Gambler Jiko Chuushinha 2 © 1992 Game Arts - Gameplay
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
Gambler Jiko Chuushinha 2: Gekitou Tokyo Mahjong Land Hen is a Miscellaneous game, developed by Yellow Horn Co and published by Game Arts, which was released in Japan in 1992.
